title: Value of Arsenal FC 's jersey sponsorship 2009 to 2020
yAxis: Jersey sponsorship revenue in million GBP
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Jersey sponsorship revenue in million GBP. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
In general Jersey sponsorship revenue in million GBP has rose over the Year.

Jersey sponsorship revenue in million GBP is roughly constant from 2009/10_(Fly_Emirates) to 2012/13_(Fly_Emirates), gradually increasing from 2012/13_(Fly_Emirates) to 2013/14_(Fly_Emirates), and finally roughly constant from 2013/14_(Fly_Emirates) to 2019/20_(Fly_Emirates).
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2012/13_(Fly_Emirates) and 2013/14_(Fly_Emirates).
Maximum Jersey sponsorship revenue in million GBP, about 40.0 was reported at Year 2018/19_(Fly_Emirates), and 2019/20_(Fly_Emirates)
The lowest Jersey sponsorship revenue in million GBP, of value 5.5 was reported at Year 2009/10_(Fly_Emirates),  2010/11_(Fly_Emirates),  2011/12_(Fly_Emirates), and 2012/13_(Fly_Emirates)
